introduction and full functioning of the 116 000 hotline for missing children and the child 
alert mechanisms (2011-2012). 
</p>
<p>9. Supporting Member States and other stakeholders in strengthening prevention, 
empowerment and participation of children to make the most of online technologies and 
counter cyber-bullying behaviour, exposure to harmful content, and other online risks 
